   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Enhancing Livelihood for 100 poor women in Bia B.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">FOWAC invests in women and girls&apos;. Organizes functional groups; promotes modern farming; gender Equity; mental well-being; diversifies economic activities; climate change advocacy to ease their plight and to improve quality of life. Enhancing livelihood project (ELP) will be executed in Northern Uganda to boost food security, income, climate smart farming for 100 female grassroots small Holder Survival farmers; to rebuild their livelihood after the two decade of civil war in the region.</narrative>
  </description>
